{
  "stem": "5810.4",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I mean, there were at that point, Belgians, Gentile Belgians, to me, were trash.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "What they had done, what they had permitted to do, what they had allowed the government to do, what these people were doing willingly.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And many, many, many Jews, I had found out, were, were taken in by Belgians at that point [INAUDIBLE] that denounced them and so on.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "If I could take advantage of them and owe them money, that's exactly what we were going to do.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we did that for about four, or five, or six different places.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We just ran from place, to place, to place until we decided, well, we have to eat and be a little more steady.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And if our family is to find us again, we better be a little more permanent someplace.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And, although I was quite young at the time, so was my sister, you were able to finally begin to get jobs.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Not, not as we know it today, not applying for it, but in what we would call sweatshops today.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I did get work in-- I must have been about 11 years old-- in what they call a false jewelry sweatshop, where you worked by the piece.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "You only got paid on however many pieces you made.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I guess I developed a pretty good skill, and I was making a lot of pieces and I was making some money.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "1945.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, that was my first of many jobs after that.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I guess at the jewelery factory, maybe a year or so.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Then just about anything that could come up.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Odd jobs, odd work.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Asking people if they wanted the sidewalk swept.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Or, you know, things of that sort, menial jobs anywhere.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So did my sister.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
